                        <lb n="4v5=83" break="no"/>rīkṛta-kanaka-gir<choice><sic>ī</sic><corr>i</corr></choice>-samunnati-vibhavam atiramaṇīyañ cūḷā-maṇi-varmma-vihāram-adhiva
